    "ailments_description": "The most common ailments you can heal with Valeriana officinalis are insomnia, stress and anxiety, which are alleviated by its sedative and anxiolytic properties. Additionally, its muscle relaxant properties help with restlessness and muscle spasms, while its carminative properties relieve digestive issues such as irritable bowel syndrome and indigestion. Valeriana officinalis is also used to treat sleep disorders and hypertension, as it has been shown to lower blood pressure and regulate sleep patterns. Its antispasmodic properties make it effective in treating menstrual cramps, migraines and headaches, as well as rheumatism and joint pain. Furthermore, it helps alleviate nervousness, irritability, panic disorder, epilepsy, restless leg syndrome, menopausal symptoms, PMS, and depression by reducing anxiety and promoting relaxation.",
